data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This 2.5yr old two-story residence offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a HUGE backyard for entertaining. Inside, a beautiful home office with French doors and built in shelves awaits you, followed by an open floor plan connecting a well-designed kitchen, breakfast room, dining room, and living room—perfect for family gatherings. There is plenty of cabinet space, beautiful granite counter tops and a well thought-out and remodeled pantry. The primary suite downstairs ensures a serene escape, and the bathroom boasts of double sinks and a separate tub and shower. The upper level features 3 bedrooms, a spacious game room, and media room. The expansive backyard is an outdoor oasis, ideal for relaxation and entertainment. Whether you're ready to BBQ, start gardening or have plans for a future pool, this backyard has the space you need and is one of the largest lots in the neighborhood. Don't miss out on seeing this one —schedule a showing today!
